1. Right-Aligned Triangle
Output
      *
    * *
  * * *
* * * *
Example 1 (Core Logic)
for(int i = 1; i <= 4; i++){
    for(int space = 1; space <= 4 - i; space++){
        System.out.print("  ");
    }
    for(int j = 1; j <= i; j++){
        System.out.print("* ");
    }
    System.out.println();
}
